  Some Chrysler products door hindges are glued on, not welded, bolted or
riveted.
Also on the new Chevy trucks the beds are glued together, again no rivets,
spot welds or bolts.
  I couldn't believe this myself till I went to my friends body shop and
watched them GLUE on the side of the pick-up bed!
  They have special equipment to undo the glue and to apply it. I trird to
split one of the glued seams on the old bed and it wouldn't budge. Techo has
come a long way!

ronnie

